# Fumadocs Integration

This documentation site is built using Fumadocs, a documentation framework for Next.js.

## Configuration
- Fumadocs configuration is defined in [source.config.ts](mdc:source.config.ts)
- The main source configuration is also available in [.source/source.config.mjs](mdc:.source/source.config.mjs)

## Content Processing
- Fumadocs processes MDX content from the [content/docs](mdc:content/docs) directory
- The content is transformed through the source processor defined in [.source/index.ts](mdc:.source/index.ts)

## Layout and Theming
- Documentation layout is configured in [src/app/layout.config.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.config.tsx)
- The main layout is defined in [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx)
- Styling is handled through Tailwind CSS with Fumadocs preset

## Documentation Features
- Search functionality is provided by Fumadocs
- Table of contents, navigation, and other documentation features are automatically generated
- Custom MDX components can be defined in [src/mdx-components.tsx](mdc:src/mdx-components.tsx)
